<plot>This bittersweet romantic comedy explores love, loyalty, success and friendship with an ensemble cast of dreamers and cynics on the eve of their friends' wedding. Harold, the most sensitive and level-headed of his friends, is in love with his best friend's girl. Complicating matters is the fact that he will be the best man at their wedding the next day, the Groom is missing, and the Bride is frantic. Things might not be the same by sunrise.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?013950</url></doc>
